    'this_is_a_unique_code_for_your_organisation'                                                                                                                     => 'fr_This is a unique code for your organisation generated from the Registration Agency and Registration Number entered. <br><br><a href="http://iatistandard.org/en/guidance/preparing-organisation/organisation-account/how-to-create-your-iati-organisation-identifier/" target="_blank">Click here for more information.</a>',
